2. Purpose of the App
This application is designed to assist users in promoting a healthy lifestyle by tracking their physical activities, including steps and distance walked. The data collected will be used solely for visualizing the user's progress, generating health reports, and providing encouragement or feedback.

3. Data Access and Usage
With your explicit consent, we access your health data (e.g., step count, walking distance) via the Huawei Health Kit API. The data is used for:
Generating personal health statistics;
Displaying historical activity trends;
Providing personalized feedback and motivational content.
We do not collect or store any personally identifiable information without your permission. All data processing takes place in compliance with relevant data protection laws.

